📊 E-Commerce Sales Analysis Dashboard (Power BI)
🚀 Project Overview

This project presents an end-to-end Power BI dashboard designed to analyze e-commerce sales data. It enables stakeholders to gain meaningful insights into sales performance, customer behavior, and business trends, supporting data-driven decision-making.

🎯 Key Features

📈 Interactive dashboard for tracking sales, profit, orders, and customer trends

🔍 Dynamic filtering using slicers and visual controls

📊 Well-structured KPIs for quick business insights

🎨 Clean and intuitive UI/UX for better data storytelling

⚡ Real-time exploration of data through interactive visuals

🛠️ Tools & Technologies

Power BI Desktop

Power Query (Data Cleaning & Transformation)

DAX (Data Analysis Expressions)

Data Visualization Techniques

Dashboard UI/UX Design

🔄 Data Processing Workflow

Connected and imported data from multiple sources

Cleaned and transformed raw data using Power Query

Modeled data for efficient analysis

Created calculated columns and measures using DAX

📌 Key KPIs

💰 Total Revenue

📊 Profit Margin

🛒 Average Order Value

📈 Sales Growth

📊 Dashboard Highlights

Sales performance analysis across different dimensions

Customer purchasing behavior insights

Trend analysis for business growth

Interactive filters for deep data exploration

💡 Business Impact

Helps identify high-performing products and regions

Improves understanding of customer behavior

Supports strategic decision-making with actionable insights
